@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> ProcessingQuery: User submits plot desc
ProcessingQuery --> FetchingRAGContext: Agent invokes Tool (RAG)
FetchingRAGContext --> ProcessingQuery: Context returned
ProcessingQuery --> FetchingIMDBData: Agent needs poster
FetchingIMDBData --> ProcessingQuery: IMDB Data returned
ProcessingQuery --> PresentingRecommendation: Final agent generation
PresentingRecommendation --> AwaitingFeedback: Wait for user match response
AwaitingFeedback --> FeedbackRecorded: User thumbs up/down
FeedbackRecorded --> Idle: Ready for next refinement

PresentingRecommendation --> ProcessingQuery: User provides follow-up context

@enduml
